WITH movie_details AS (
    SELECT 
        t.id AS movie_id,
        t.title AS movie_title,
        t.production_year,
        k.keyword AS movie_keyword,
        c.name AS company_name,
        ct.kind AS company_type,
        a.name AS actor_name,
        r.role AS actor_role
    FROM 
        aka_title t
    JOIN 
        movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
    JOIN 
        keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
    JOIN 
        movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
    JOIN 
        company_name c ON mc.company_id = c.id
    JOIN 
        company_type ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id
    JOIN 
        complete_cast cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id
    JOIN 
        cast_info ci ON cc.subject_id = ci.person_id AND cc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
    JOIN 
        aka_name a ON ci.person_id = a.person_id
    JOIN 
        role_type r ON ci.role_id = r.id
    WHERE 
        t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2023
        AND k.keyword LIKE '%action%'
        AND c.country_code = 'USA'
)
SELECT 
    md.movie_title,
    md.production_year,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT md.actor_name, ', ') AS actors,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT md.movie_keyword, ', ') AS keywords,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT md.company_name || ' (' || md.company_type || ')', ', ') AS companies
FROM 
    movie_details md
GROUP BY 
    md.movie_id, md.movie_title, md.production_year
ORDER BY 
    md.production_year DESC, md.movie_title

SELECT COALESCE("t6"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t6"."MOVIE_TITLE") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "t6"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t6"."ACTORS", "t6"."KEYWORDS", "t6"."COMPANIES"
FROM (SELECT "t2"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "t2"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTORS", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "t0"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "t1"."name" || ' (' || "company_type"."kind" || ')', ', ') AS "COMPANIES"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "keyword"
WHERE "keyword" LIKE '%action%') AS "t0"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "t0"."id" = "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
INNER JOIN ("role_type" INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id") ON "role_type"."id" = "cast_info"."role_id" INNER JOIN ("company_type" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "company_name"
WHERE "country_code" = 'USA') AS "t1" INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "t1"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_id") ON "company_type"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_type_id" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "s1"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000 AND "production_year" <= 2023) AS "t2" INNER JOIN "complete_cast" ON "t2"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id") ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "t2"."id") ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "complete_cast"."subject_id" AND "cast_info"."movie_id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id") ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "t2"."id"
GROUP BY "t2"."id", "t2"."title", "t2"."production_year"
ORDER BY "t2"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t2"."title") AS "t6"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "movie_id", "subject_id", "status_id"
FROM "complete_cast"

SELECT COALESCE("t6"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t6"."MOVIE_TITLE") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "t6"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t6"."ACTORS", "t6"."KEYWORDS", "t6"."COMPANIES"
FROM (SELECT "t2"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "t2"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTORS", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "t0"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "t1"."name" || ' (' || "company_type"."kind" || ')', ', ') AS "COMPANIES"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "keyword"
WHERE "keyword" LIKE '%action%') AS "t0"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "t0"."id" = "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
INNER JOIN ("role_type" INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id") ON "role_type"."id" = "cast_info"."role_id" INNER JOIN ("company_type" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "company_name"
WHERE "country_code" = 'USA') AS "t1" INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "t1"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_id") ON "company_type"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_type_id" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "aka_title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000 AND "production_year" <= 2023) AS "t2" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "t2"."id" = "s1"."movie_id") ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "t2"."id") ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "s1"."subject_id" AND "cast_info"."movie_id" = "s1"."movie_id") ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "t2"."id"
GROUP BY "t2"."id", "t2"."title", "t2"."production_year"
ORDER BY "t2"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t2"."title") AS "t6"
